Both files written. Here's what was built:

---

**DriftSync** prototype at `/prototypes/2026-03-21-driftsync/App.tsx`

**Design system:**
- Deep navy (`#0C0B18`) base with a radial violet gradient ambient glow
- Primary: `#7C6FFF` (soft violet), Secondary: `#4ECDC4` (teal), Accent: `#FFB347` (amber), Danger: `#FF6B8A`
- Inter font, dark glassmorphism cards with subtle borders

**4 screens:**

| Tab | Content |
|-----|---------|
| **Today** | Unfinished Business digest — live progress bar, moment-match nudge card, checkable task list with type badges & urgency pills |
| **Capture** | Text / Voice / Photo mode switcher — live textarea with save confirmation, animated recording pulse, recent captures with cluster labels |
| **Clusters** | Accordion groups — Reply Later, Buy on Next Outing, Do When Home, Meeting Follow-ups — each expandable with source/age metadata |
| **Moments** | Time-window cards with context chips (Commuting · 3 min free) — matched micro-tasks with effort estimates, active moment has "Start Now" CTA |

**Interactions:** check-off animation with strikethrough, save-feedback flash, voice recording pulse ring, tab press spring scale, cluster expand/collapse, Start Now toggle state.
